flowchart TD
    A[Call Connects] --> B[Identify Caller]
    B --> C[Retrieve Pending Notifications]
    C --> D[Read Notification Aloud]
    D --> E{Caller Response}
    E -->|Acknowledge| F[Mark as Acknowledged]
    E -->|Needs Help| G[Flag for Follow-Up]
    F --> H{More Items?}
    G --> H
    H -->|Yes| D
    H -->|No| I[End Call with Summary]
